sections.heading: of slaughter livestock; violations; penalties
sections.text: Any person, firm, corporation, or association, or any agent thereof, who shall violate the provisions of sections 54-1809 to 54-1811, shall be guilty of a Class II misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1975, LB 436, ยง 3;Laws 1977, LB 39, ยง 48.
